## Banned vocabulary (Go identifiers)

Do NOT revive these as type / var / method names:

`Marker` (type), `MasterGeneral`, `Layer2`, `Analyst`, `ChiefAnalyst`

Allowed: FE chart label field `Marker string` with `json:"marker"` (wire contract only).

Canonical names: `Frame`, `Runtime`, `streaming` / `snapshot`, `ScoreDecision`, `ScoreFactor`.

